# hexa-lang /.own — project-local SSOT layer (monotonic strengthening of hive .raw)
# 포맷: raw-format (.raw 와 동일 파서). 자세한 스펙: self/raw_loader.hexa
# 검증: ./build/hexa_stage0 tool/own_lint.hexa
#
# (빈 body — hexa-lang local rules 추가 시 own N <status> "<name>" + slug + enforce + why 형식)

own 1 live "parser format stability — raw_loader.hexa is API contract"
  slug parser-format-stability
  enforce self/raw_cli.hexa verify
  scope self/raw_loader.hexa
  why raw_loader.hexa is consumed by hive + nexus + airgenome + (self). Parser surface changes break cross-repo SSOT parsing — backward-compat semver applies.

own 2 live "AOT cache GC ω-cycle policy (raw 7 of L7 commit fcd087f0c)"
  slug aot-cache-policy
  enforce tool/aot_cache_gc.hexa
  scope .hexa-cache/
  why touch-on-access + prob 1% + audit ledger; lossless ω-cycle GC. project-local because cache layout is hexa-lang implementation detail.
